com.epam.jwd.task01.logic

Class GemstoneListCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.jwd.task01.logic.GemstoneListCreator

  • public class GemstoneListCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    Base method to create and add into list GemstoneList instances of Gemstone

    Each GemstoneList is based on Arraylist collection and able to use all relevant methods.

    Each element of GemstoneList has restrictions on some fields values. For example, negative and zero values are prohibited for the fields, containing weight and price. Attempting to add an ineligible value throws an unchecked IllegalArgumentException. This check is performed by Validator class.

    See Also:
    ArrayList, GemstoneValidator
